Package: robotstxt
Type: Package
Title: A 'robots.txt' Parser and 'Webbot'/'Spider'/'Crawler' Permissions Checker
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R: c(
        person(
          "Peter", "Meissner", role = c("aut", "cre"),
          email = "retep.meissner@gmail.com"
        ),
	      person("Oliver", "Keys", role = "ctb"),
	      person("Rich", "Fitz John", role = "ctb")
	      )
Description: Provides a simple functionality to parse and check
    'robots.txt' files. Data fields are provided as
    data frames and vectors. Permissions can be checked by providing
    path character vectors and optional bot names.
